ions to the $\\Lambda$ single-particle\npotential is repulsive at higher densities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Feb 2018 02:14:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Mar 2018 14:32:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-14"}
