ut. We complement our results with an\nempirical evaluation of our algorithm on real world datasets, and show that it\nperforms well empirically even using simple off-the-shelf predictions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Feb 2018 04:30:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Jul 2018 21:42:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2019 15:50:02 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 21 Aug 2020 14:36:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-24"}
