 number of lanes and\ncope with lane changes. We verify our method on the tuSimple dataset and\nachieve competitive results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Feb 2018 15:09:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-16"}
